  <title>What else do world clocks show?</title>

  <p>Apart from checking the time, you can also view the sunrise and sunset
  times for today. You will also see if the city is a day behind or ahead of
  you.</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Press the <gui style="button">World</gui> button.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Select a city to view more information about it.</p>
    </item>
